	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Ideas for powerpack NSF player</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My idea is to play them like virtuaNES does with the exact style with the keyboard and everything. And about the expansions well don't display them but instead display track/track and the controls are simple A=advance track, B=previous track&lt;=disable triangle, &gt;=disable PCM, UP=disable wave 1, Down=disable wave 2, Start=Start/pause, Select=disable noise, and reset brings you to the NSF menu while power brings you to the main menu. There are no volume nor speed controllers as of yet.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


