	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In order to disable channels or run visualization when playing NSF directly on 2A03 hardware, the program would have to patch all writes to $4000-$4017 with calls to vis code in the player. Speed control would probably be easier.

		

		</td>
